quote: The race was basically mixed with age group men, the start was quite hilly and technical so I found myself in a group of 15-20 men already after 15km.
Breakaway with two, gambled on my sprint after a fast race but unfortunately one guy was faster. Nevertheless time for a well deserved off-season and let's bring the hunger for victory towards 2026.

We came here to test ourselves on one of the toughest courses in the series and to secure a ticket to Nannup. The climbs never stopped and the technical sections made it a real gravel classic. I'm proud of the team and excited to represent at the world championships next year.
